name: Disposition of revenues
text: §200-34  Disposition of revenues.  All fees and penalties collected pursuant to sections 200-10, 200-14, 200-14.5, 200-25, and 200-32, and all fees and penalties established by rules adopted pursuant to sections 200-4 and 200-24, shall be deposited in the boating special fund. [L 1991, c 272, pt of §2; am L 2005, c 126, §2]
